0e9rable \u00e0 un d\u00e9ni de service \u00e0 distance.", "title": "Vuln\u00e9rabilit\u00e9 dans OpenSSH", "vendor_advisories": [{"published_at": "2024-07-01", "title": "Bulletin de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 OpenSSH", "url": "https://www.openssh.com/txt/release-9.8"}]}